Area of Expertise: Elon Musk co-founded and leads Tesla, SpaceX, Neuralink and The Boring Company. As the co-founder and CEO of Tesla, Elon leads all product design, engineering and global manufacturing of the company's electric vehicles, battery products and solar energy products.

Bio: Adam Silver is an American lawyer and sports executive who is the fifth and current commissioner of the National Basketball Association.

Bio: Paul Clifton Anthony George is an American professional basketball player for the Los Angeles Clippers of the National Basketball Association.
